# Repo Rules

## 1. Scaffolding & Code Organization

- Turborepo monorepo should be used to manage this project.
- This project will be deployed to vercel consider this when configuring project files.
- The ./packages/ directory in this repo's root is where code that is shared between packages should live.
- All config files that can be shared between apps should be organizaed logically in a config package.